name: Kisss Bar Vienna
description: Gay-friendly Lounge Bar & Club with food service, Art Corner for artists, spacious outdoor area, and elegant gold-accented interior. Features themed nights (80s/90s), drag queen bingo, and live music events.

name: Vorspiel
description: Cozy and intimate LGBTQ+ cocktail bar in Vienna's Neubau district. Known for friendly atmosphere, creative drink menu, and perfect spot for relaxed evenings or casual date nights.

name: Augenblick
description: LGBT-friendly café-bar with mixed clientele in a traditional historical 19th-century building. Run by former Cheri owners, features beautiful terrace, game evenings, and vernissages.

name: Café Rifugio
description: Small friendly gay café bar beloved by Vienna's mature local crowd. Features warm atmosphere, delicious affordable wine, and daily happy hour with specially priced drink of the day.

name: The Hive
description: Renovated and redesigned successor to Red Carpet bar. Largest queer pub in the district featuring dance floor in cellar, brand-new outdoor area, coffees, cocktails, and Austrian cuisine until 21:00.

name: Palmenhaus
description: Gay-friendly brasserie, café and bar housed in a stunning Jugendstil glasshouse (former imperial greenhouse from 1822) in the Burggarten. Features 15-meter high ceilings, exotic plants, and Friday DJ sets.

name: Flinte
description: Queer-feminist bar and cultural venue for FLINT persons only (Frauen, Lesben, Inter, Non-binary, Trans). Volunteer-run collective space since 1977 with live music, DJ nights, readings, and political discussions.
opening_hours: Fri 19:00-24:00, check Facebook for additional events

name: Café Savoy
description: Historic gay-friendly Viennese coffeehouse dating back to imperial times on Naschmarkt. Features Europe's largest mirrors outside Versailles, baroque decor, and pleasant outdoor terrace.

name: Café Willendorf
description: Queer community café and restaurant at the Türkis Rosa Lila Villa. Offers tasty cakes from Fett+Zucker, vegetarian-heavy lunch and dinner menus, cocktails, and famous Queen's Brunch with drag performances on Sundays.

name: Café Rüdiger
description: Gay bar and café operating Friday and Saturday nights from midnight. Known for welcoming atmosphere and regular gay events in Vienna's 5th district.
